-white font-semibold","children":"Shipbuilding:"}]," BusinessKorea (248 vs. 48 carrier deliveries, 2021-2025), VesselsValue (orderbook data, $71.3B backlog)."]}],["$","p","4",{"className":"font-[family-name:var(--font-sans)] text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.7] mb-3","style":{"color":"var(--color-muted)"},"children":[["$","strong","0",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Semiconductor supply chain:"}]," USGS 2026 Mineral Commodity Summaries (Qatar at 33.2% of world helium production), Korea International Trade Association (64.7% helium dependency), Counterpoint Research (SK Hynix 62% HBM, Q2 2025), TrendForce, J2 Sourcing, DiscoveryAlert."]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"font-[family-name:var(--font-sans)] text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.7] mb-3","style":{"color":"var(--color-muted)"},"children":[["$","strong","0",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"GPU and data centre TCO:"}]," SemiAnalysis, Introl, Lenovo Press, Spheron benchmarks."]}],["$","p","6",{"className":"font-[family-name:var(--font-sans)] text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.7] mb-3","style":{"color":"var(--color-muted)"},"children":[["$","strong","0",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Cost-transmission model:"}]," Directional estimates, not precise forecasts. Actual pass-through depends on contract structures, inventory positions, and competitive dynamics that vary by company. The scenario framework (60-day / 6-month / 3-5 year) is calibrated against available data and acknowledges significant uncertainty at longer durations."]}],["$","p","7",{"className":"font-[family-name:var(--font-sans)] text-[0.85rem] leading-[1.7] mb-3","style":{"color":"var(--color-muted)"},"children":["$L1e"]}],"$L1f","$L20"]]}]
